# System Design Document: Real-Time Collaborative Document Editor

## 1. Executive Summary

This document outlines the system design for a real-time collaborative document editor capable of supporting 100,000 concurrent users. The system enables multiple users to simultaneously edit documents with real-time synchronization, conflict resolution, and high availability.

### Key Requirements
- Support 100K concurrent users
- Real-time collaboration with sub-second latency
- Conflict-free document synchronization
- High availability (99.9% uptime)
- Horizontal scalability
- Data consistency and persistence

## 2. High-Level Architecture

